name: wtv020-dfplayer

HJDCukOT8.content:
Welcomme to the WTV020 MP3 Player

At first specify RX/TX GPIO Ports
This Node works with Software UART
Do not use SerialPort Pins of your Board.
So you can use Tweak Nodes, GPIO and Debug at same time.

INIT-> Initialize UART Communication
Delay-> After INIT Time (Delay) you can use all Functions
Pulse Inputs-> like Play is self-explantory.

Track-> here u can take 0-2999
EQ->
     0 Normal
     1 Pop
     2 Rock
     3 Jazz
     4 Classic
     5 Base

On CF Card:

Track-> Tracke named 001, 002, 003 max. 2999
